  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Trump Simulator 2025' is a silly little game made by a silly little person. For the lols.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself into the role of the President Elect!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run the country while flying in <strong>Air Force One</strong>, thousands of feet in the air.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nuke anyone you don't like</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass whatever laws you want</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive your CyberSuck vehicle </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your Secret Service agents get you Cola at 3am</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tweet crazy things</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Book hot dates with pornstars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore your trans identity</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is your second and final term, and you're making the most of it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But don't forget to report back to your boss: the mysterious 'Mr. Musk' or he might punish you like a bad girl...</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Trump Simulator 2025' is a silly little game made by a silly little person. For the lols.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself into the role of the President Elect!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run the country while flying in <strong>Air Force One</strong>, thousands of feet in the air.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nuke anyone you don't like</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass whatever laws you want</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive your CyberSuck vehicle </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your Secret Service agents get you Cola at 3am</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tweet crazy things</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Book hot dates with pornstars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore your trans identity</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is your second and final term, and you're making the most of it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But don't forget to report back to your boss: the mysterious 'Mr. Musk' or he might punish you like a bad girl...</p>",
